{"tid":30514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【特首選戰】獲鍾逸傑轉軚支持 葉劉：CY好大量唔會介意","createTime":"2016-12-09T08:11:42.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T13:37:12.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8e4168db6f44cb2d85c5528ef378824c9f856999","tid":30514,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T08:11:42.000Z","msg":"4年前為梁振英站台助選的前布政司鍾逸傑，表態支持新民黨主席葉劉淑儀參選，葉劉淑儀以一身綠衫現身立法會，被問到對鍾逸傑表態支持她參選特首有何感覺時，指「我好感謝佢，佢係我舊上司，我跟咗佢好多年，好感謝佢一路都支持我的工作」，認同今次鍾逸傑是為她打了一支「強心針」，「我好鼓舞」。<br />\n<br />\n問到鍾逸傑上屆曾任梁振英競選顧問，今屆改為支持她，會否擔心梁振英不開心時，葉劉指「呢點係佢老人家（鍾逸傑）的決定，我相信梁生都係一個好大量的人，唔會介意的」。葉劉又重申，自己至今仍然是弱勢，「我地位比較低，比起傳媒時時提及嗰啲名，我地位比較低啦，咁有啲人認為女性係無可能出到、做到（特首）呢個位，所以我仍然好弱勢、要努力」。<br />\n<br />\n問到其前下屬黃鴻超和盛智文均支持她參選，葉劉指，盛智文過去一直支持她很久，2007年立法會「兩太之戰」，盛智文都支持她，為她站台，「我同佢好傾得埋，所以好感謝呢兩個朋友」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56024197&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56024197%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161209&d=1rSek3WAoaz9K%2BTt8VLqCwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=039ad17a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56024197%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161209&h=45bbf084\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56024197&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161209</a>"},{"pid":"03e5eac1300529433fc725f00908e2a6e888b196","tid":30514,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T08:11:51.000Z","msg":"跳船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d220fc44b4ec5e4910835569f5fcb977ef9fe90f","tid":30514,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:12:35.000Z","msg":"葉劉肯定係另一個梁振英，如果佢宣傳參選，一定要全力反對。"},{"pid":"c30009a81fee295b380ab2c1cebb83795f9211b2","tid":30514,"uid":49609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:24:50.000Z","msg":"鍾逸傑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a865ac42efc760779ec950270fdfe7fd922f636","tid":30514,"uid":30743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T10:56:56.000Z","msg":"選舉這樣難  我卻這樣啱<br />\n<br />\n仍然能受鍾逸傑的稱讚<br />\n<br />\n請給我負擔"},{"pid":"c7d34f371e561f0d26caad4d7cc6fa92eafac756","tid":30514,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:02:04.000Z","msg":"鍾逸傑呢條前殖民地奶共狗<br />\n好心97就返祖國安享晚年<br />\n宜家下海降grade同班支那人整到周身屎都唔知為乜 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d6f9668e3c5ffa8811b076a9223d21efd2ee7f1","tid":30514,"uid":1900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T13:20:36.000Z","msg":"跳得咁急呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小心太重呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n沉就唔係幾好啦<br />\n人地重係船仔黎咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"329c872a530cf24504d07d520c5b35a293e2e166","tid":30514,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T13:24:18.000Z","msg":"梁特咁小氣，會唔會有黑材料睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"133958d2db10d517ec35061d72c5d0d5d7c5579f","tid":30514,"uid":5603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T13:29:37.000Z","msg":"應該會係鬍鬚掛....<br />\n葉劉...冇可能🤔🤔"},{"pid":"0ea18e04be7a0dffc314e19e11812d74c2e9091b","tid":30514,"uid":2867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T13:37:12.000Z","msg":"上次高登仔都支持689 <br />\n今次咁快就反葉瘤 邊有可能"}]}